# 🧩 Task Manager Django Project

A **Django-based REST API** that allows users to register, log in, and manage their daily tasks.  
It includes **JWT authentication**, **user management**, and **task tracking** features — built with clean, modular code and ready for integration with a React or mobile frontend.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ User registration and authentication (JWT)
- ✅ Create, read, update, and delete tasks
- ✅ Role-based access (Admin / User)
- ✅ API built with Django REST Framework
- ✅ Filtering and pagination support
- ✅ Secure authentication using `SimpleJWT`
- ✅ Easily connectable to React frontend

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Category | Tools |
|-----------|-------|
| **Backend** | Python 3, Django, Django REST Framework |
| **Authentication** | Simple JWT |
| **Database** | SQLite (default) |
| **Filtering** | django-filter |
| **Environment Management** | venv |
| **Frontend (Optional)** | React.js or React Native |

